Order = namedtuple('Order', ['price', 'amount'])

#,        (orderbook)
def gen_read_quotes(file_path):
    inFile = open(file_path, 'r', encoding='utf8')
    #       
    *info, lot, price_step = inFile.readline().split(':')
    lot = int(lot) if lot else 1
    price_step = float(price_step) if price_step else None
    
    #   
    orderbook = None

    while True:
        line = inFile.readline()
        if line.split(': ')[0] == 'Received': #      (     )
            if orderbook: #     ,   
                yield orderbook

            time_str = line.split(': ')[1].strip()
            time = datetime.datetime.strptime(time_str, '%d.%m.%Y %H:%M:%S.%f')

            orderbook = {'Received': time, 'Bid': [], 'Ask': []} #     
        elif line != '': #    
            try: #       orderbook
                deal_type, price, volume = line.strip().split(';')
                price, volume = float(price), int(volume)

                if deal_type == 'Ask' or deal_type == 'BestAsk':
                    orderbook['Ask'].append(Order(price, volume*lot))
                elif deal_type == 'Bid' or deal_type == 'BestBid':
                    orderbook['Bid'].append(Order(price, volume*lot))
                else:
                    pass
            except: #  
                continue
        else: #  ,    
            break
    inFile.close()

Deal = namedtuple('Deal', ['received', 'type', 'price', 'amount'])

#,       (deal)
def gen_read_deals(file_path):
    inFile = open(file_path, 'r', encoding='utf8')
    #       
    *info, lot, price_step = inFile.readline().split(':')
    lot = int(lot) if lot else 1
    price_step = float(price_step) if price_step else None
    
    while True:
        line = inFile.readline()
        if line:
            try: #       
                received, exch_time, deal_id, deal_type, price, volume, OI = line.strip().split(';')
                received = datetime.datetime.strptime(received, '%d.%m.%Y %H:%M:%S.%f')
                price = float(price)
                amount = int(volume)*lot
                deal = Deal(received, deal_type, price, amount)
                yield deal
            except: #  
                continue
        else: #  ,    
            break
    inFile.close()

#1.2)     
def relative_volume(deals_file, T, info): #T - timedelta (), info -    
    #    ,   
    inFile = open(deals_file, 'r', encoding='utf8')
    connection_type, ticker, share_type, lot, price_step = inFile.readline().strip().split(':')
    inFile.close()
    
    if ticker in info.keys(): #      ,     
        #            free float
        n = info[ticker].n
        f = info[ticker].free_float
        
        #    
        day_start = datetime.time(hour=10, minute=0, second=0, microsecond=0)
        day_end = datetime.time(hour=18, minute=40, second=0, microsecond=0)

        time_checkpoint = None
        Q = 0 #volume
        for deal in gen_read_deals(deals_file):
            if not time_checkpoint: #    time_checkpoint,   
                time_checkpoint = datetime.datetime.combine(deal.received.date(), day_start) + T

            if deal.received.time() < day_start or deal.received.time() > day_end: #    day_start   day_end,  
                continue
            else:
                if deal.received < time_checkpoint: #    time_checpoint'a,     
                    Q += deal.amount
                else: #  time_checkpoint    
                    yield Coef(time_checkpoint, round(Q/(f*n), 8))
                    time_checkpoint = time_checkpoint + T
                    Q = 0
        else:
            last_checkpoint = datetime.datetime.combine(time_checkpoint.date(), day_end)
            yield Coef(last_checkpoint, round(Q/(f*n), 8))

def relative_value(deals_file, T, info): #T - timedelta (), info -    
    #    ,   
    inFile = open(deals_file, 'r', encoding='utf8')
    connection_type, ticker, share_type, lot, price_step = inFile.readline().strip().split(':')
    inFile.close()
    
    if ticker in info.keys(): #      ,     
        #            free float
        n = info[ticker].n
        f = info[ticker].free_float
        
        #    
        day_start = datetime.time(hour=10, minute=0, second=0, microsecond=0)
        day_end = datetime.time(hour=18, minute=40, second=0, microsecond=0)

        time_checkpoint = None
        V = 0 #value
        for deal in gen_read_deals(deals_file):
            if not time_checkpoint: #    time_checkpoint,   
                time_checkpoint = datetime.datetime.combine(deal.received.date(), day_start) + T

            if deal.received.time() < day_start or deal.received.time() > day_end: #    day_start   day_end,  
                continue
            else:
                if deal.received < time_checkpoint: #    time_checpoint'a,     
                    V += deal.amount*deal.price
                    last_price = deal.price
                else: #  time_checkpoint    
                    yield Coef(time_checkpoint, round(V/(last_price*f*n), 8))
                    time_checkpoint = time_checkpoint + T
                    V = 0
                    last_price = deal.price
        else:
            last_checkpoint = datetime.datetime.combine(time_checkpoint.date(), day_end)
            yield Coef(last_checkpoint, round(V/(last_price*f*n), 8))

def relative_spread(quotes_file, T):
    #    
    day_start = datetime.time(hour=10, minute=0, second=0, microsecond=0)
    day_end = datetime.time(hour=18, minute=40, second=0, microsecond=0)
    
    time_checkpoint = None
    Sspread = 0 #spreads sum
    Nspread = 0 #spreads count
    for orderbook in gen_read_quotes(quotes_file):
        if not time_checkpoint: #    time_checkpoint,   
            time_checkpoint = datetime.datetime.combine(orderbook['Received'].date(), day_start) + T
        
        if orderbook['Received'].time() < day_start or orderbook['Received'].time() > day_end: #  orderbook   day_start   day_end,  
            continue
        else:
            if orderbook['Received'] < time_checkpoint: #    time_checpoint'a
                try: #    (..        )
                    midpoint = (orderbook['Ask'][-1].price + orderbook['Bid'][0].price)/2
                    Sspread += (orderbook['Ask'][-1].price - orderbook['Bid'][0].price)/midpoint
                    Nspread += 1
                except: # 
                    continue
            else: #    time_checpoint'a,   time_checkpoint,       Sspread  Nspread 
                spread = Sspread/Nspread if Nspread != 0 else None
                yield Coef(time_checkpoint, round(spread, 8))
                time_checkpoint = time_checkpoint + T
                midpoint = (orderbook['Ask'][-1].price + orderbook['Bid'][0].price)/2
                Sspread = (orderbook['Ask'][-1].price - orderbook['Bid'][0].price)/midpoint
                Nspread = 1
    else:
        spread = Sspread/Nspread if Nspread != 0 else None
        last_checkpoint = datetime.datetime.combine(time_checkpoint.date(), day_end)
        yield Coef(last_checkpoint, round(spread, 8))

#8.1)   
def deals_count(deals_file, T): #T - timedelta ()
    #    
    day_start = datetime.time(hour=10, minute=0, second=0, microsecond=0)
    day_end = datetime.time(hour=18, minute=40, second=0, microsecond=0)

    time_checkpoint = None
    N = 0 #count
    for deal in gen_read_deals(deals_file):
        if not time_checkpoint: #    time_checkpoint,   
            time_checkpoint = datetime.datetime.combine(deal.received.date(), day_start) + T
        
        if deal.received.time() < day_start or deal.received.time() > day_end: #    day_start   day_end,  
            continue
        else:
            if deal.received < time_checkpoint: #    time_checpoint'a,   
                N += 1
            else: #  time_checkpoint   
                yield Coef(time_checkpoint, N)
                time_checkpoint = time_checkpoint + T
                N = 0
    else:
        last_checkpoint = datetime.datetime.combine(time_checkpoint.date(), day_end)
        yield Coef(last_checkpoint, N)

#9.1)       ( )
def deals_timeout(deals_file, T): #T - timedelta ()
    #    
    day_start = datetime.time(hour=10, minute=0, second=0, microsecond=0)
    day_end = datetime.time(hour=18, minute=40, second=0, microsecond=0)
    
    time_checkpoint = None
    prev_deal_time = None
    Stheta = 0 #timeouts sum
    Ntheta = 0 #timeouts count
    for deal in gen_read_deals(deals_file):
        if not time_checkpoint: #    time_checkpoint,   
            time_checkpoint = datetime.datetime.combine(deal.received.date(), day_start) + T
        if not prev_deal_time: #       ,       
            prev_deal_time = datetime.datetime.combine(deal.received.date(), day_start)
            
        if deal.received.time() < day_start or deal.received.time() > day_end: #    day_start   day_end,  
            continue
        else:
            if deal.received < time_checkpoint: #    time_checpoint'a,    
                Stheta += (deal.received - prev_deal_time).total_seconds()
                Ntheta += 1
                prev_deal_time = deal.received
            else: #  time_checkpoint,        Stheta  Ntheta 
                theta = Stheta/Ntheta if Ntheta != 0 else None
                yield Coef(time_checkpoint, round(theta, 8))
                time_checkpoint = time_checkpoint + T
                Stheta = (deal.received - prev_deal_time).total_seconds()
                Ntheta = 1
                prev_deal_time = deal.received
    else:
        theta = Stheta/Ntheta if Ntheta != 0 else None
        last_checkpoint = datetime.datetime.combine(time_checkpoint.date(), day_end)
        yield Coef(last_checkpoint, round(theta, 8))

def LOGQS(quotes_file, T):
    #    
    day_start = datetime.time(hour=10, minute=0, second=0, microsecond=0)
    day_end = datetime.time(hour=18, minute=40, second=0, microsecond=0)
    
    time_checkpoint = None
    SLOGQS = 0 #LOGQS sum
    NLOGQS = 0 #LOGQS count
    for orderbook in gen_read_quotes(quotes_file):
        if not time_checkpoint: #    time_checkpoint,   
            time_checkpoint = datetime.datetime.combine(orderbook['Received'].date(), day_start) + T
        
        if orderbook['Received'].time() < day_start or orderbook['Received'].time() > day_end: #  orderbook   day_start   day_end,  
            continue
        else:
            if orderbook['Received'] < time_checkpoint: #    time_checpoint'a
                try: #    (..        )
                    numerator = log(orderbook['Ask'][-1].price) - log(orderbook['Bid'][0].price)
                    denominator = log(orderbook['Ask'][-1].amount) + log(orderbook['Bid'][0].amount)
                    SLOGQS += numerator/denominator if denominator != 0 else 0
                    NLOGQS += 1
                except: # 
                    continue
            else: #    time_checpoint'a,   time_checkpoint,   LOGQS    SLOGQS  NLOGQS 
                LOGQS = SLOGQS/NLOGQS if NLOGQS != 0 else None
                yield Coef(time_checkpoint, round(LOGQS, 8))
                time_checkpoint = time_checkpoint + T
                numerator = log(orderbook['Ask'][-1].price) - log(orderbook['Bid'][0].price)
                denominator = log(orderbook['Ask'][-1].amount) + log(orderbook['Bid'][0].amount)
                SLOGQS = numerator/denominator if denominator != 0 else 0
                NLOGQS = 1
    else:
        LOGQS = SLOGQS/NLOGQS if NLOGQS != 0 else None
        last_checkpoint = datetime.datetime.combine(time_checkpoint.date(), day_end)
        yield Coef(last_checkpoint, round(LOGQS, 8))
